T1  - A note on nonstationarity, structural breaks, and the Fisher effect
AU  - Malliaropulos, Dimitrios
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 24
IS  - 5
SP  - 695
EP  - 707
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/05/01/
