T1  - Cross- and delta-hedges: Regression- versus price-based hedge ratios
AU  - Sercu, Piet
AU  - Wu, Xueping
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 24
IS  - 5
SP  - 735
EP  - 757
PY  - 2000
